Country age structures

Source: R/data.R
age_structure.Rd

A dataset containing the proportions of individuals in each of twenty 5-year age groups. The variables are as follows:

age_structure

Format

A data with frame with 200 rows and 21 variables:

ID_0

GADM administrative unit level 0 code

band_0_4

proportion of individuals of age 0-4

band_5_9

proportion of individuals of age 5-9

band_10_14

proportion of individuals of age 10-14

band_15_19

proportion of individuals of age 15-19

band_20_24

proportion of individuals of age 20-24

band_25_29

proportion of individuals of age 25-20

band_31_34

proportion of individuals of age 31-34

band_35_39

proportion of individuals of age 35-39

band_40_44

proportion of individuals of age 40-44

band_45_49

proportion of individuals of age 45-49

band_50_54

proportion of individuals of age 50-54

band_55_59

proportion of individuals of age 55-59

band_60_64

proportion of individuals of age 60-64

band_65_69

proportion of individuals of age 65-69

band_70_74

proportion of individuals of age 70-74

band_75_79

proportion of individuals of age 75-79

band_80_84

proportion of individuals of age 80-84

band_85_89

proportion of individuals of age 85-89

band_90_94

proportion of individuals of age 90-94
